parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to hesitate or refuse to accelerate, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates to accelerate
the transmission slips or hesitates to shift gears
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear
the check engine light illuminates
the transmission overheats
and the vehicle makes an abnormal noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to shut off unexpectedly, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle shuts off unexpectedly
the battery drains
and the ignition only works part of the time.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Stabiltrak system can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The Stabiltrak system warning light illuminates
the vehicle hesitates to accelerate
and the vehicle makes an abnormal noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the timing chain can cause the engine to stall or fail, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine stalls or fails
the check engine light illuminates
and the vehicle makes an abnormal noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to seize or become extremely difficult to turn, making it challenging to control the vehicle, especially at low speeds. This can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The steering wheel is hard to turn
the steering wheel seizes
the power steering pump fails
the steering wheel vibrates or shakes
unusual noises when turning
and difficulty turning at low speeds.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become difficult to control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power
stalls
or hesitates to shift gears
the transmission slips or hesitates
unusual noises when shifting
and difficulty accelerating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the failure of the airbags to deploy in the event of a crash, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light remains illuminated
the "Service Airbag" message appears on the dashboard
the passenger airbag sensor fails to recognize a passenger
the airbag system malfunctions
the airbag warning light turns on and off intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger seat occupant sensor can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the failure of the airbags to deploy in the event of a crash, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The passenger airbag sensor fails to recognize a passenger
the airbag warning light remains illuminated
the "Service Airbag" message appears on the dashboard
the airbag system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the vehicle to become difficult to steer, leading to loss of control and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The power steering system locks or becomes difficult to steer
the power steering system makes a whining or rubbing noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the trunk liftgate can cause injury or damage to people or objects.
symptoms: The trunk liftgate suddenly lowers or closes unexpectedly
the trunk liftgate fails to open or close properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various malfunctions, including loss of power, failure of the airbag system, and failure of the anti-lock braking system, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The radio
chimes
and OnStar system may not work
the backup camera may not function
the airbag warning light may illuminate
the vehicle may not start
and the doors may not lock or unlock.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The water leak can cause electrical system failures, mold, rust, and mildew, which can lead to health issues and safety hazards.
symptoms: Water leaks into the vehicle through the sunroof
top of the windshield area
and driver's side floor area
causing water to accumulate on the floorboards
in the dashboard
and in the electrical components.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the liftgate can cause inconvenience, damage to the vehicle, and potential safety hazards.
symptoms: The liftgate may not open or close properly
may make noise
or may not respond to the remote control or dashboard buttons.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Ignition Switch and Key Fob Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch and key fob can cause the vehicle to stall, not start, or not allow the key to be removed from the ignition, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle may not start
the key may not turn to the off position
the key may be stuck in the ignition
or the vehicle may stall while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag warning light may illuminate
the airbag may deploy unexpectedly
or the airbag may not deploy in the event of an accident.
